1. *Steve* je bio najbolji učenik u školi. (*Steve* was the best student in the school.)
2. *Steve* je odrastao u srećnoj porodici. (*Steve* grew up in a happy family.)
3. *Steveovo* ponašanje često je dovodilo njegove roditelje u nezgodnu situaciju. (*Steve's* behaviour often put his parents in an awkward situation.)
4. *Steveov* otac je uvek stajao iza njega. (*Steve's* father always stood behind him.)
5. *Steve* je uvek bio marljiv i spreman za rad. (*Steve* was always hardworking and ready for work.)